reviewText: This is the most wonderful excercise tape. Mine quit working. I have had it for many years. It is very effective and I am thrilled to have found it on Amazon, I plan to order it as soon as I finish this review. It is low impact and I felt upset when I put it in the player this week and it wouldn't work. Anita
Probably my favorite ab workout. Liza's voice isn't annoying, she isn't super energetic and the moves she does seem to make sense.
